[Dementia, a progressive disease: severe dementia. Identification of end-stage 
dementia].

[Article in Spanish]

Formiga F(1), Robles MJ, Fort I.

Author information:
(1)Unidad de Geriatría, Servicio de Medicina Interna, Hospital Universitari de 
