Diagnosis and management of Marfan syndrome.

von Kodolitsch Y(1), Rybczynski M, Detter C, Robinson PN.

Author information:
(1)University Hospital Hamburg, Centre of Cardiology & Cardiovascular Surgery, 
Department of Cardiology/Angiology, University Hospital Hamburg-Eppendorf, 
